title: Godspower Oriamhen’s Resume
text:
Business Analytics Major, Computer Information Technology Minor.





I am a dedicated Business Analytics Major, passionate about transforming raw data into meaningful insights. My academic background, coupled with hands-on experience, has equipped me with a robust skill set in data analysis, statistical modeling, and strategic decision-making.


I am trying to leverage my analytical skills to drive business success. Passionate about finding innovative solutions to complex problems, I am eager to contribute to the evolving landscape of data-driven decision-making. I thrive in collaborative environments where diverse perspectives converge to solve challenges. Whether working with cross-functional teams or engaging in insightful discussions, I believe in the power of collaboration to achieve exceptional results. In the dynamic field of business analytics, staying ahead requires a commitment to continuous learning. I am dedicated to keeping my skills sharp and staying informed about emerging trends in data analytics and business intelligence.



Data Science, Data Analysis, Business Analysis, Transforming data into actionable insights.




2021-2025 Brigham Young University - Idaho
